Package com.jlranta.pholiotracker.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StockApi
    StockApi is an interface that describes how the support for various stock APIs should be implemented.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlphaVantageApi
    This class implements the Alpha Vantage stock API.
    RestApiQuery
    RestApiQuery class is a helper class for placing HTTP queries to the stock APIs.
    StockApiHandler
    Initializes and handles all the APIs that implement the StockApi interface.
    StockSearchApi
    The StockSearchApi can be used for translating company names to stock symbols that should be used in the stock API queries.
    StockSearchResult
    Describes a single search result.
    TestApi
    This is a dummy API for testing purposes.
